<view class="container">
  <image src="http://localhost:5001/images/recipe/01.jpg" class="recipe-image" mode="aspectFill" />
  <view class="recipe-info">
    <text class="recipe-title">清炖盐池滩羊肉</text>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">所需食材</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ing-list">
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">花椒 10-20颗</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">大葱段</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">厚姜片 5-10片</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">山药</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">青萝卜</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">粗盐适量</text></view>
        <view class="ing-item"><text class="ing-dot">·</text><text class="ing-name">香菜少许</text></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-block">
      <view class="section-header">
        <view class="section-bar"></view>
        <text class="section-title">烹饪步骤</text>
      </view>
      <view class="step-list">
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>1</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">750g 清炖羊肉洗净入锅（最好是砂锅、土锅等适合煲汤的锅），一次性加足水，尽量避免中途加水，以免影响汤味。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>2</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">羊肉汤开锅后撇去浮沫，加入除盐以外的所有调味料。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>3</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">转中小火煲 40 分钟左右，加入山药或青萝卜等配菜煮熟。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="step-item">
          <view class="step-num"><text>4</text></view>
          <text class="step-text">酌情加盐，出锅撒上香菜即可。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>